{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775875178746,"sessionID":"ses_2859c9bcbffes4sOhzPY4OWWic","part":{"id":"prt_d7a68c068001U4ik97rkpV0pN0","messageID":"msg_d7a6436820012BavTvEJepga6V","sessionID":"ses_2859c9bcbffes4sOhzPY4OWWic","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_tool-fde0b90fca39453f9c67244f2732ffcb","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"content":"# Proposal: AR-026 — K8s/AgentCube Provider\n\n## 概述\n\n本文档针对 AgentCube CLI 项目中的 Kubernetes 提供商系统进行架构提案。该提案旨在规范和完善两种部署提供商——标准 Kubernetes (k8s) 和 AgentCube CRD (agentcube) 的实现，确保 CLI 工具能够灵活地将 AI 代理部署到不同的 Kubernetes 环境。\n\n## 背景\n\n当前 AgentCube CLI 项目已经实现了基础的 Kubernetes 部署功能，包括：\n\n- `KubernetesProvider` 类：使用标准 Kubernetes Deployment 和 NodePort Service 部署\n- `AgentCubeProvider` 类：使用 AgentRuntime 自定义资源部署\n- CLI 命令集成：publish、invoke、status 支持提供商选择\n- Kubernetes Python 客户端集成\n\n然而，在代码审查和实际使用中发现了一些需要改进的方面：\n\n1. **错误处理不一致**：两个提供商的错误处理逻辑存在差异\n2. **状态监控不完整**：缺乏统一的状态查询和健康检查机制\n3. **配置管理复杂**：两个提供商的配置参数和验证逻辑分散\n4. **扩展性受限**：添加新提供商需要修改核心代码\n5. **测试覆盖不足**：缺乏完整的单元测试和集成测试\n\n## 当前实现分析\n\n### KubernetesProvider 现状\n\n```python\nclass KubernetesProvider:\n    def __init__(\n        self,\n        namespace: str = \"default\",\n        verbose: bool = False,\n        kubeconfig: Optional[str] = None,\n    ) -> None: ...\n\n    def deploy_agent(\n        self,\n        agent_name: str,\n        image_url: str,\n        port: int,\n        entrypoint: Optional[str] = None,\n        replicas: int = 1,\n        node_port: Optional[int] = None,\n        env_vars: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None,\n    ) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n\n    def get_agent_status(self, agent_name: str) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n    def delete_agent(self, agent_name: str) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n```\n\n**功能特性**：\n- 创建 Deployment 和 NodePort Service\n- 支持副本数配置\n- 等待部署就绪（默认 120 秒超时）\n- 名称消毒（符合 Kubernetes 命名规范）\n- 命名空间自动创建\n\n### AgentCubeProvider 现状\n\n```python\nclass AgentCubeProvider:\n    def __init__(\n        self,\n        namespace: str = \"default\",\n        verbose: bool = False,\n        kubeconfig: Optional[str] = None,\n    ) -> None: ...\n\n    def deploy_agent_runtime(\n        self,\n        agent_name: str,\n        image_url: str,\n        port: int,\n        entrypoint: Optional[str] = None,\n        env_vars: Optional[Dict[str, str]] = None,\n        workload_manager_url: Optional[str] = None,\n        router_url: Optional[str] = None,\n        readiness_probe_path: Optional[str] = None,\n        readiness_probe_port: Optional[int] = None,\n    ) -> Dict[str, Any]: ...\n\n    def get_agent_runtime(self, name: str, namespace: str) -> Optional[Dict[str, Any]]: ...\n```\n\n**功能特性**：\n- 创建 AgentRuntime 自定义资源\n- CRD API: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n- 配置工作负载管理器和路由器 URL\n- 健康探针配置\n- 会话超时设置\n\n## 问题陈述\n\n### 1. 接口不一致\n\n两个提供商的方法签名和返回值存在差异：\n\n- **方法名称**：`deploy_agent` vs `deploy_agent_runtime`\n- **参数名称**：`agent_name` vs `name`（在 `get_agent_runtime` 中）\n- **返回值结构**：`KubernetesProvider` 返回详细的部署信息，`AgentCubeProvider` 仅返回基本状态\n- **状态查询**：`get_agent_status` vs `get_agent_runtime`\n\n这导致：\n- 调用方需要针对不同提供商编写不同的代码\n- 难以实现统一的错误处理\n- 代码维护成本高\n\n### 2. 错误处理不完善\n\n当前错误处理存在以下问题：\n\n- **超时处理**：`wait_for_deployment_ready` 超时后直接抛出异常，没有重试机制\n- **部分失败**：删除操作忽略 404 错误，但没有日志记录\n- **错误信息**：错误消息不够详细，难以调试\n- **异常类型**：使用通用的 `ApiException`，缺乏自定义异常\n\n### 3. 状态监控缺失\n\n当前实现缺乏以下功能：\n\n- **实时状态更新**：部署后无法实时监控资源状态\n- **事件查询**：无法查询 Pod 事件和日志\n- **健康检查**：缺乏自定义健康检查机制\n- **资源使用监控**：无法监控 CPU、内存使用情况\n\n### 4. 配置验证不足\n\n两个提供商的配置验证逻辑分散：\n\n- **参数验证**：某些参数没有进行前置验证\n- **依赖检查**：没有检查依赖资源是否存在\n- **环境变量**：环境变量读取逻辑重复\n- **默认值**：默认值配置不统一\n\n### 5. 扩展性受限\n\n当前架构存在以下扩展性限制：\n\n- **硬编码 API**：CRD API 信息硬编码在代码中\n- **提供商选择**：添加新提供商需要修改 CLI 代码\n- **插件系统**：缺乏插件机制支持自定义提供商\n- **配置驱动**：无法通过配置文件自定义提供商行为\n\n## 提案方案\n\n### 1. 统一提供商接口\n\n#### 1.1 定义基类接口\n\n```python\nfrom abc import ABC, abstractmethod\nfrom typing import Any, Dict, List, Optional\nfrom dataclasses import dataclass\nfrom enum import Enum\n\nclass ProviderStatus(str, Enum):\n    \"\"\"提供商状态枚举\"\"\"\n    PENDING = \"pending\"\n    DEPLOYING = \"deploying\"\n    RUNNING = \"running\"\n    FAILED = \"failed\"\n    NOT_FOUND = \"not_found\"\n    ERROR = \"error\"\n\n@dataclass\nclass DeploymentResult:\n    \"\"\"部署结果数据类\"\"\"\n    status: ProviderStatus\n    agent_name: str\n    namespace: str\n    resource_url: Optional[str] = None\n    metadata: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = None\n    error: Optional[str] = None\n\n@dataclass\nclass AgentStatus:\n    \"\"\"代理状态数据类\"\"\"\n    status: ProviderStatus\n    agent_name: str\n    namespace: str\n    replicas: Optional[int] = None\n    ready_replicas: Optional[int] = None\n    available_replicas: Optional[int] = None\n    resource_type: Optional[str] = None\n    metadata: Optional[Dict[str, Any]] = None\n    error: Optional[str] = None\n\nclass BaseProvider(ABC):\n    \"\"\"提供商基类\"\"\"\n\n    def __init__(\n        self,\n        namespace: str = \"default\",\n        verbose: bool = False,\n        kubeconfig: Optional[str] = None,\n        timeout: int = 120,\n    ) -> None:\n        \"\"\"初始化提供商\n\n        Args:\n            namespace: 命名空间\n            verbose: 是否启用详细日志\n            kubeconfig: kubeconfig 文件路径\n            timeout: 操作超时时间（秒）\n        \"\"\"\n        self.namespace = namespace\n        self.verbose = verbose\n        self.kubeconfig = kubeconfig\n        self.timeout = timeout\n\n    @abstractmethod\n    def deploy(\n        self,\n        agent_name: str,\n        image_url: str,\n        port: int,\n        **kwargs: Any,\n    ) -> DeploymentResult:\n        \"\"\"部署代理\n\n        Args:\n            agent_name: 代理名称\n            image_url: 容器镜像 URL\n            port: 容器端口\n            **kwargs: 其他提供商特定的参数\n\n        Returns:\n            DeploymentResult: 部署结果\n        \"\"\"\n        pass\n\n    @abstractmethod\n    def get_status(self, agent_name: str) -> AgentStatus:\n        \"\"\"获取代理状态\n\n        Args:\n            agent_name: 代理名称\n\n        Returns:\n            AgentStatus: 代理状态\n        \"\"\"\n        pass\n\n    @abstractmethod\n    def delete(self, agent_name: str) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n        \"\"\"删除代理\n\n        Args:\n            agent_name: 代理名称\n\n        Returns:\n            Dict[str, Any]: 删除结果\n        \"\"\"\n        pass\n\n    @abstractmethod\n    def get_provider_type(self) -> str:\n        \"\"\"获取提供商类型\n\n        Returns:\n            str: 提供商类型（如 \"k8s\" 或 \"agentcube\"）\n        \"\"\"\n        pass\n\n    def validate_config(self, **kwargs: Any) -> List[str]:\n        \"\"\"验证配置参数\n\n        Args:\n            **kwargs: 配置参数\n\n        Returns:\n            List[str]: 错误消息列表，空列表表示验证通过\n        \"\"\"\n        return []\n\n    def _sanitize_name(self, name: str) -> str:\n        \"\"\"消毒名称，符合 Kubernetes 命名规范\n\n        Args:\n            name: 原始名称\n\n        Returns:\n            str: 消毒后的名称\n        \"\"\"\n        import re\n        sanitized = re.sub(r\"[^a-z0-9-]\", \"-\", name.lower())\n        sanitized = re.sub(r\"-+\", \"-\", sanitized)\n        sanitized = sanitized.strip(\"-\")\n        if len(sanitized) > 63:\n            sanitized = sanitized[:63].rstrip(\"-\")\n        return sanitized or \"agent\"\n```\n\n#### 1.2 重构 KubernetesProvider\n\n```python\nclass KubernetesProvider(BaseProvider):\n    \"\"\"标准 Kubernetes 提供商\"\"\"\n\n    def __init__(\n        self,\n        namespace: str = \"default\",\n        verbose: bool = False,\n        kubeconfig: Optional[str] = None,\n        timeout: int = 120,\n    ) -> None:\n        super().__init__(namespace, verbose, kubeconfig, timeout)\n        self._load_kubernetes_config()\n        self._core_v1 = client.CoreV1Api()\n        self._apps_v1 = client.AppsV1Api()\n\n    def get_provider_type(self) -> str:\n        return \"k8s\"\n\n    def deploy(\n        self,\n        agent_name: str,\n        image_url: str,\n        port: int,\n        **kwargs: Any,\n    ) -> DeploymentResult:\n        \"\"\"部署代理到标准 Kubernetes\"\"\"\n        try:\n            self._ensure_namespace()\n\n            sanitized_name = self._sanitize_name(agent_name)\n\n            # 提取参数\n            replicas = kwargs.get(\"replicas\", 1)\n            node_port = kwargs.get(\"node_port\")\n            env_vars = kwargs.get(\"env_vars\")\n\n            # 验证配置\n            config_errors = self.validate_config(replicas=replicas, node_port=node_port)\n            if config_errors:\n                return DeploymentResult(\n                    status=ProviderStatus.ERROR,\n                    agent_name=agent_name,\n                    namespace=self.namespace,\n                    error=f\"Configuration validation failed: {'; '.join(config_errors)}\",\n                )\n\n            # 创建 Deployment\n            self._create_deployment(\n                sanitized_name, image_url, port, replicas, env_vars\n            )\n\n            # 创建 Service\n            service = self._create_service(sanitized_name, port, node_port)\n\n            # 等待就绪\n            self._wait_for_ready(sanitized_name, self.timeout)\n\n            return DeploymentResult(\n                status=ProviderStatus.RUNNING,\n                agent_name=agent_name,\n                namespace=self.namespace,\n                resource_url=f\"http://localhost:{service.spec.ports[0].node_port}\",\n                metadata={\n                    \"deployment_name\": sanitized_name,\n                    \"service_name\": sanitized_name,\n                    \"replicas\": replicas,\n                    \"node_port\": service.spec.ports[0].node_port,\n                },\n            )\n\n        except Exception as e:\n            logger.error(f\"Failed to deploy agent {agent_name}: {e}\")\n            return DeploymentResult(\n                status=ProviderStatus.FAILED,\n                agent_name=agent_name,\n                namespace=self.namespace,\n                error=str(e),\n            )\n\n    def get_status(self, agent_name: str) -> AgentStatus:\n        \"\"\"获取代理状态\"\"\"\n        sanitized_name = self._sanitize_name(agent_name)\n\n        try:\n            deployment = self._apps_v1.read_namespaced_deployment(\n                sanitized_name, self.namespace\n            )\n\n            return AgentStatus(\n                status=ProviderStatus.RUNNING,\n                agent_name=agent_name,\n                namespace=self.namespace,\n                resource_type=\"Deployment\",\n                replicas=deployment.spec.replicas,\n                ready_replicas=deployment.status.ready_replicas or 0,\n                available_replicas=deployment.status.available_replicas or 0,\n            )\n\n        except ApiException as e:\n            if e.status == 404:\n                return AgentStatus(\n                    status=ProviderStatus.NOT_FOUND,\n                    agent_name=agent_name,\n                    namespace=self.namespace,\n                )\n            return AgentStatus(\n                status=ProviderStatus.ERROR,\n                agent_name=agent_name,\n                namespace=self.namespace,\n                error=str(e),\n            )\n\n    def delete(self, agent_name: str) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n        \"\"\"删除代理\"\"\"\n        sanitized_name = self._sanitize_name(agent_name)\n\n        results = {}\n\n        try:\n            self._apps_v1.delete_namespaced_deployment(sanitized_name, self.namespace)\n            results[\"deployment\"] = \"deleted\"\n            logger.info(f\"Deleted deployment {sanitized_name}\")\n        except ApiException as e:\n            if e.status != 404:\n                logger.warning(f\"Failed to delete deployment: {e}\")\n                results[\"deployment\"] = f\"failed: {e}\"\n\n        try:\n            self._core_v1.delete_namespaced_service(sanitized_name, self.namespace)\n            results[\"service\"] = \"deleted\"\n            logger.info(f\"Deleted service {sanitized_name}\")\n        except ApiException as e:\n            if e.status != 404:\n                logger.warning(f\"Failed to delete service: {e}\")\n                results[\"service\"] = f\"failed: {e}\"\n\n        return {\n            \"status\": \"deleted\",\n            \"agent_name\": agent_name,\n            \"namespace\": self.namespace,\n            \"details\": results,\n        }\n\n    def validate_config(self, **kwargs: Any) -> List[str]:\n        \"\"\"验证配置参数\"\"\"\n        errors = []\n\n        replicas = kwargs.get(\"replicas\", 1)\n        if not isinstance(replicas, int) or replicas < 0:\n            errors.append(\"replicas must be a non-negative integer\")\n\n        node_port = kwargs.get(\"node_port\")\n        if node_port is not None:\n            if not isinstance(node_port, int) or not (30000 <= node_port <= 32767):\n                errors.append(\"node_port must be between 30000 and 32767\")\n\n        return errors\n\n    # ... 其他辅助方法保持不变 ...\n```\n\n#### 1.3 重构 AgentCubeProvider\n\n```python\nclass AgentCubeProvider(BaseProvider):\n    \"\"\"AgentCube AgentRuntime CR 提供商\"\"\"\n\n    CR_GROUP = \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\"\n    CR_VERSION = \"v1alpha1\"\n    CR_PLURAL = \"agentruntimes\"\n\n    def __init__(\n        self,\n        namespace: str = \"default\",\n        verbose: bool = False,\n        kubeconfig: Optional[str] = None,\n        timeout: int = 120,\n    ) -> None:\n        super().__init__(namespace, verbose, kubeconfig, timeout)\n        self._load_kubernetes_config()\n        self._custom_api = CustomObjectsApi()\n\n    def get_provider_type(self) -> str:\n        return \"agentcube\"\n\n    def deploy(\n        self,\n        agent_name: str,\n        image_url: str,\n        port: int,\n        **kwargs: Any,\n    ) -> DeploymentResult:\n        \"\"\"部署代理使用 AgentRuntime CR\"\"\"\n        try:\n            self._ensure_namespace()\n\n            sanitized_name = self._sanitize_name(agent_name)\n\n            # 提取参数\n            entrypoint = kwargs.get(\"entrypoint\")\n            env_vars = kwargs.get(\"env_vars\")\n            workload_manager_url = kwargs.get(\"workload_manager_url\") or os.getenv(\"WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL\")\n            router_url = kwargs.get(\"router_url\") or os.getenv(\"ROUTER_URL\")\n            readiness_probe_path = kwargs.get(\"readiness_probe_path\", \"/health\")\n            readiness_probe_port = kwargs.get(\"readiness_probe_port\", port)\n\n            # 验证配置\n            config_errors = self.validate_config(\n                workload_manager_url=workload_manager_url,\n                router_url=router_url,\n            )\n            if config_errors:\n                return DeploymentResult(\n                    status=ProviderStatus.ERROR,\n                    agent_name=agent_name,\n                    namespace=self.namespace,\n                    error=f\"Configuration validation failed: {'; '.join(config_errors)}\",\n                )\n\n            # 创建或更新 AgentRuntime CR\n            cr = self._build_agent_runtime_cr(\n                sanitized_name, image_url, port, entrypoint, env_vars,\n                workload_manager_url, router_url,\n                readiness_probe_path, readiness_probe_port,\n            )\n\n            self._apply_agent_runtime_cr(sanitized_name, cr)\n\n            return DeploymentResult(\n                status=ProviderStatus.RUNNING,\n                agent_name=agent_name,\n                namespace=self.namespace,\n                metadata={\n                    \"cr_name\": sanitized_name,\n                    \"workload_manager_url\": workload_manager_url,\n                    \"router_url\": router_url,\n                },\n            )\n\n        except Exception as e:\n            logger.error(f\"Failed to deploy agent {agent_name}: {e}\")\n            return DeploymentResult(\n                status=ProviderStatus.FAILED,\n                agent_name=agent_name,\n                namespace=self.namespace,\n                error=str(e),\n            )\n\n    def get_status(self, agent_name: str) -> AgentStatus:\n        \"\"\"获取代理状态\"\"\"\n        sanitized_name = self._sanitize_name(agent_name)\n\n        try:\n            cr = self._custom_api.get_namespaced_custom_object(\n                group=self.CR_GROUP,\n                version=self.CR_VERSION,\n                namespace=self.namespace,\n                plural=self.CR_PLURAL,\n                name=sanitized_name,\n            )\n\n            # 从 CR status 中读取状态\n            status_data = cr.get(\"status\", {})\n\n            return AgentStatus(\n                status=ProviderStatus.RUNNING,\n                agent_name=agent_name,\n                namespace=self.namespace,\n                resource_type=\"AgentRuntime\",\n                metadata={\n                    \"agent_endpoint\": status_data.get(\"agentEndpoint\"),\n                    \"cr_status\": status_data,\n                },\n            )\n\n        except ApiException as e:\n            if e.status == 404:\n                return AgentStatus(\n                    status=ProviderStatus.NOT_FOUND,\n                    agent_name=agent_name,\n                    namespace=self.namespace,\n                )\n            return AgentStatus(\n                status=ProviderStatus.ERROR,\n                agent_name=agent_name,\n                namespace=self.namespace,\n                error=str(e),\n            )\n\n    def delete(self, agent_name: str) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n        \"\"\"删除代理\"\"\"\n        sanitized_name = self._sanitize_name(agent_name)\n\n        try:\n            self._custom_api.delete_namespaced_custom_object(\n                group=self.CR_GROUP,\n                version=self.CR_VERSION,\n                namespace=self.namespace,\n                plural=self.CR_PLURAL,\n                name=sanitized_name,\n            )\n            logger.info(f\"Deleted AgentRuntime {sanitized_name}\")\n            return {\n                \"status\": \"deleted\",\n                \"agent_name\": agent_name,\n                \"namespace\": self.namespace,\n                \"cr_name\": sanitized_name,\n            }\n        except ApiException as e:\n            if e.status == 404:\n                return {\n                    \"status\": \"not_found\",\n                    \"agent_name\": agent_name,\n                    \"namespace\": self.namespace,\n                }\n            logger.error(f\"Failed to delete AgentRuntime {sanitized_name}: {e}\")\n            return {\n                \"status\": \"failed\",\n                \"agent_name\": agent_name,\n                \"namespace\": self.namespace,\n                \"error\": str(e),\n            }\n\n    def validate_config(self, **kwargs: Any) -> List[str]:\n        \"\"\"验证配置参数\"\"\"\n        errors = []\n\n        workload_manager_url = kwargs.get(\"workload_manager_url\") or os.getenv(\"WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL\")\n        router_url = kwargs.get(\"router_url\") or os.getenv(\"ROUTER_URL\")\n\n        if not workload_manager_url:\n            errors.append(\"workload_manager_url is required (provide as parameter or WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL env var)\")\n\n        if not router_url:\n            errors.append(\"router_url is required (provide as parameter or ROUTER_URL env var)\")\n\n        return errors\n\n    def _build_agent_runtime_cr(\n        self,\n        name: str,\n        image_url: str,\n        port: int,\n        entrypoint: Optional[str],\n        env_vars: Optional[Dict[str, str]],\n        workload_manager_url: str,\n        router_url: str,\n        readiness_probe_path: str,\n        readiness_probe_port: int,\n    ) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n        \"\"\"构建 AgentRuntime CR\"\"\"\n        env_list = [\n            client.V1EnvVar(name=k, value=v) for k, v in (env_vars or {}).items()\n        ]\n\n        return {\n            \"apiVersion\": f\"{self.CR_GROUP}/{self.CR_VERSION}\",\n            \"kind\": \"AgentRuntime\",\n            \"metadata\": {\n                \"name\": name,\n                \"namespace\": self.namespace,\n            },\n            \"spec\": {\n                \"image\": image_url,\n                \"port\": port,\n                \"entrypoint\": entrypoint or \"\",\n                \"env\": env_list,\n                \"workloadManagerURL\": workload_manager_url,\n                \"routerURL\": router_url,\n                \"sessionTimeout\": \"15m\",\n                \"maxSessionDuration\": \"8h\",\n                \"readinessProbe\": {\n                    \"path\": readiness_probe_path,\n                    \"port\": readiness_probe_port,\n                },\n                \"imagePullSecrets\": [{\"name\": \"default-secret\"}],\n            },\n        }\n\n    def _apply_agent_runtime_cr(self, name: str, cr: Dict[str, Any]) -> None:\n        \"\"\"应用 AgentRuntime CR（创建或更新）\"\"\"\n        try:\n            self._custom_api.create_namespaced_custom_object(\n                group=self.CR_GROUP,\n                version=self.CR_VERSION,\n                namespace=self.namespace,\n                plural=self.CR_PLURAL,\n                body=cr,\n            )\n            logger.info(f\"Created AgentRuntime {name}\")\n        except ApiException as e:\n            if e.status == 409:\n                self._custom_api.replace_namespaced_custom_object(\n                    group=self.CR_GROUP,\n                    version=self.CR_VERSION,\n                    namespace=self.namespace,\n                    plural=self.CR_PLURAL,\n                    name=name,\n                    body=cr,\n                )\n                logger.info(f\"Updated AgentRuntime {name}\")\n            else:\n                raise\n\n    # ... 其他辅助方法保持不变 ...\n```\n\n### 2. 提供商工厂\n\n```python\nfrom typing import Type\n\nclass ProviderFactory:\n    \"\"\"提供商工厂\"\"\"\n\n    _providers: Dict[str, Type[BaseProvider]] = {}\n\n    @classmethod\n    def register(cls, provider_type: str, provider_class: Type[BaseProvider]) -> None:\n        \"\"\"注册提供商\n\n        Args:\n            provider_type: 提供商类型\n            provider_class: 提供商类\n        \"\"\"\n        cls._providers[provider_type] = provider_class\n        logger.info(f\"Registered provider: {provider_type}\")\n\n    @classmethod\n    def unregister(cls, provider_type: str) -> None:\n        \"\"\"注销提供商\n\n        Args:\n            provider_type: 提供商类型\n        \"\"\"\n        if provider_type in cls._providers:\n            del cls._providers[provider_type]\n            logger.info(f\"Unregistered provider: {provider_type}\")\n\n    @classmethod\n    def create(\n        cls,\n        provider_type: str,\n        **kwargs: Any,\n    ) -> BaseProvider:\n        \"\"\"创建提供商实例\n\n        Args:\n            provider_type: 提供商类型\n            **kwargs: 提供商初始化参数\n\n        Returns:\n            BaseProvider: 提供商实例\n\n        Raises:\n            ValueError: 如果提供商类型不存在\n        \"\"\"\n        if provider_type not in cls._providers:\n            raise ValueError(f\"Unknown provider type: {provider_type}. Available: {list(cls._providers.keys())}\")\n\n        provider_class = cls._providers[provider_type]\n        return provider_class(**kwargs)\n\n    @classmethod\n    def list_providers(cls) -> List[str]:\n        \"\"\"列出所有已注册的提供商\n\n        Returns:\n            List[str]: 提供商类型列表\n        \"\"\"\n        return list(cls._providers.keys())\n\n\n# 注册默认提供商\nProviderFactory.register(\"k8s\", KubernetesProvider)\nProviderFactory.register(\"agentcube\", AgentCubeProvider)\n```\n\n### 3. 错误处理增强\n\n#### 3.1 自定义异常\n\n```python\nclass ProviderError(Exception):\n    \"\"\"提供商基础异常\"\"\"\n    pass\n\n\nclass ProviderConfigurationError(ProviderError):\n    \"\"\"提供商配置错误\"\"\"\n    pass\n\n\nclass ProviderDeploymentError(ProviderError):\n    \"\"\"提供商部署错误\"\"\"\n    pass\n\n\nclass ProviderTimeoutError(ProviderError):\n    \"\"\"提供商超时错误\"\"\"\n    pass\n\n\nclass ProviderNotFoundError(ProviderError):\n    \"\"\"提供商未找到错误\"\"\"\n    pass\n```\n\n#### 3.2 重试机制\n\n```python\nimport time\nfrom functools import wraps\nfrom typing import Callable, Type\n\ndef retry_on_exception(\n    max_attempts: int = 3,\n    delay: float = 1.0,\n    backoff: float = 2.0,\n    exceptions: Tuple[Type[Exception], ...] = (Exception,),\n) -> Callable:\n    \"\"\"重试装饰器\n\n    Args:\n        max_attempts: 最大尝试次数\n        delay: 初始延迟（秒）\n        backoff: 延迟倍增因子\n        exceptions: 需要重试的异常类型\n\n    Returns:\n        Callable: 装饰后的函数\n    \"\"\"\n    def decorator(func: Callable) -> Callable:\n        @wraps(func)\n        def wrapper(*args: Any, **kwargs: Any) -> Any:\n            last_exception = None\n            current_delay = delay\n\n            for attempt in range(max_attempts):\n                try:\n                    return func(*args, **kwargs)\n                except exceptions as e:\n                    last_exception = e\n                    if attempt < max_attempts - 1:\n                        logger.warning(\n                            f\"Attempt {attempt + 1}/{max_attempts} failed: {e}. \"\n                            f\"Retrying in {current_delay}s...\"\n                        )\n                        time.sleep(current_delay)\n                        current_delay *= backoff\n                    else:\n                        logger.error(f\"All {max_attempts} attempts failed\")\n\n            raise last_exception  # type: ignore\n\n        return wrapper\n    return decorator\n\n\n# 在 KubernetesProvider 中使用\nclass KubernetesProvider(BaseProvider):\n    @retry_on_exception(\n        max_attempts=3,\n        delay=2.0,\n        exceptions=(ApiException,),\n    )\n    def _wait_for_ready(self, name: str, timeout: int) -> None:\n        \"\"\"等待部署就绪（带重试）\"\"\"\n        start_time = time.time()\n\n        while time.time() - start_time < timeout:\n            try:\n                deployment = self._apps_v1.read_namespaced_deployment(name, self.namespace)\n                if (\n                    deployment.status.ready_replicas is not None\n                    and deployment.status.ready_replicas >= deployment.spec.replicas\n                ):\n                    logger.info(f\"Deployment {name} is ready\")\n                    return\n            except ApiException as e:\n                logger.warning(f\"Error checking deployment status: {e}\")\n\n            time.sleep(2)\n\n        raise ProviderTimeoutError(\n            f\"Deployment {name} did not become ready within {timeout} seconds\"\n        )\n```\n\n### 4. 状态监控增强\n\n```python\nfrom typing import List, Dict, Any, Optional\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\n\nclass StatusMonitor:\n    \"\"\"状态监控器\"\"\"\n\n    def __init__(\n        self,\n        provider: BaseProvider,\n        agent_name: str,\n        poll_interval: int = 5,\n    ) -> None:\n        \"\"\"初始化状态监控器\n\n        Args:\n            provider: 提供商实例\n            agent_name: 代理名称\n            poll_interval: 轮询间隔（秒）\n        \"\"\"\n        self.provider = provider\n        self.agent_name = agent_name\n        self.poll_interval = poll_interval\n        self._monitoring = False\n\n    def monitor(\n        self,\n        duration: Optional[int] = None,\n        callback: Optional[Callable[[AgentStatus], None]] = None,\n    ) -> List[AgentStatus]:\n        \"\"\"监控代理状态\n\n        Args:\n            duration: 监控持续时间（秒），None 表示无限\n            callback: 状态回调函数\n\n        Returns:\n            List[AgentStatus]: 状态历史\n        \"\"\"\n        self._monitoring = True\n        status_history: List[AgentStatus] = []\n\n        start_time = datetime.now()\n\n        while self._monitoring:\n            try:\n                status = self.provider.get_status(self.agent_name)\n                status_history.append(status)\n\n                if callback:\n                    callback(status)\n\n                # 检查是否应该停止\n                if status.status in [ProviderStatus.FAILED, ProviderStatus.ERROR]:\n                    logger.error(f\"Agent {self.agent_name} failed or errored\")\n                    break\n\n                if duration and (datetime.now() - start_time).total_seconds() >= duration:\n                    break\n\n            except Exception as e:\n                logger.error(f\"Error monitoring agent {self.agent_name}: {e}\")\n\n            time.sleep(self.poll_interval)\n\n        self._monitoring = False\n        return status_history\n\n    def stop(self) -> None:\n        \"\"\"停止监控\"\"\"\n        self._monitoring = False\n\n    def wait_for_status(\n        self,\n        target_status: ProviderStatus,\n        timeout: int = 120,\n    ) -> AgentStatus:\n        \"\"\"等待代理达到目标状态\n\n        Args:\n            target_status: 目标状态\n            timeout: 超时时间（秒）\n\n        Returns:\n            AgentStatus: 最终状态\n\n        Raises:\n            ProviderTimeoutError: 超时\n        \"\"\"\n        start_time = datetime.now()\n\n        while (datetime.now() - start_time).total_seconds() < timeout:\n            status = self.provider.get_status(self.agent_name)\n\n            if status.status == target_status:\n                return status\n\n            if status.status in [ProviderStatus.FAILED, ProviderStatus.ERROR]:\n                raise ProviderError(\n                    f\"Agent {self.agent_name} failed or errored: {status.error}\"\n                )\n\n            time.sleep(self.poll_interval)\n\n        raise ProviderTimeoutError(\n            f\"Agent {self.agent_name} did not reach status {target_status} within {timeout} seconds\"\n        )\n\n\nclass EventMonitor:\n    \"\"\"事件监控器\"\"\"\n\n    def __init__(\n        self,\n        provider: BaseProvider,\n        agent_name: str,\n    ) -> None:\n        \"\"\"初始化事件监控器\n\n        Args:\n            provider: 提供商实例\n            agent_name: 代理名称\n        \"\"\"\n        self.provider = provider\n        self.agent_name = agent_name\n\n        if isinstance(provider, KubernetesProvider):\n            self._core_v1 = client.CoreV1Api()\n\n    def get_events(\n        self,\n        since: Optional[datetime] = None,\n    ) -> List[Dict[str, Any]]:\n        \"\"\"获取代理相关事件\n\n        Args:\n            since: 起始时间\n\n        Returns:\n            List[Dict[str, Any]]: 事件列表\n        \"\"\"\n        if not isinstance(self.provider, KubernetesProvider):\n            return []\n\n        sanitized_name = self.provider._sanitize_name(self.agent_name)\n\n        try:\n            events = self._core_v1.list_namespaced_event(\n                self.provider.namespace,\n                field_selector=f\"involvedObject.name={sanitized_name}\",\n            )\n\n            event_list = []\n            for event in events.items:\n                if since and event.last_timestamp < since:\n                    continue\n\n                event_list.append({\n                    \"type\": event.type,\n                    \"reason\": event.reason,\n                    \"message\": event.message,\n                    \"timestamp\": event.last_timestamp,\n                })\n\n            return event_list\n\n        except Exception as e:\n            logger.error(f\"Failed to get events: {e}\")\n            return []\n\n    def get_pod_logs(\n        self,\n        container_name: Optional[str] = None,\n        tail_lines: int = 100,\n    ) -> List[str]:\n        \"\"\"获取 Pod 日志\n\n        Args:\n            container_name: 容器名称\n            tail_lines: 日志行数\n\n        Returns:\n            List[str]: 日志行\n        \"\"\"\n        if not isinstance(self.provider, KubernetesProvider):\n            return []\n\n        sanitized_name = self.provider._sanitize_name(self.agent_name)\n\n        try:\n            # 获取 Pod 列表\n            pods = self._core_v1.list_namespaced_pod(\n                self.provider.namespace,\n                label_selector=f\"app={sanitized_name}\",\n            )\n\n            logs = []\n            for pod in pods.items:\n                try:\n                    pod_logs = self._core_v1.read_namespaced_pod_log(\n                        pod.metadata.name,\n                        self.provider.namespace,\n                        container=container_name,\n                        tail_lines=tail_lines,\n                    )\n                    logs.append(f\"=== Pod: {pod.metadata.name} ===\")\n                    logs.extend(pod_logs.split(\"\\n\"))\n                except Exception as e:\n                    logger.warning(f\"Failed to get logs for pod {pod.metadata.name}: {e}\")\n\n            return logs\n\n        except Exception as e:\n            logger.error(f\"Failed to get pod logs: {e}\")\n            return []\n```\n\n### 5. 配置管理优化\n\n#### 5.1 配置验证器\n\n```python\nclass ConfigValidator:\n    \"\"\"配置验证器\"\"\"\n\n    @staticmethod\n    def validate_provider_config(\n        provider_type: str,\n        **kwargs: Any,\n    ) -> List[str]:\n        \"\"\"验证提供商配置\n\n        Args:\n            provider_type: 提供商类型\n            **kwargs: 配置参数\n\n        Returns:\n            List[str]: 错误消息列表\n        \"\"\"\n        try:\n            provider = ProviderFactory.create(provider_type, verbose=False)\n            return provider.validate_config(**kwargs)\n        except Exception as e:\n            return [f\"Failed to validate config: {e}\"]\n\n    @staticmethod\n    def validate_k8s_config(\n        replicas: Optional[int] = None,\n        node_port: Optional[int] = None,\n    ) -> List[str]:\n        \"\"\"验证 Kubernetes 配置\n\n        Args:\n            replicas: 副本数\n            node_port: NodePort\n\n        Returns:\n            List[str]: 错误消息列表\n        \"\"\"\n        errors = []\n\n        if replicas is not None:\n            if not isinstance(replicas, int) or replicas < 0:\n                errors.append(\"replicas must be a non-negative integer\")\n\n        if node_port is not None:\n            if not isinstance(node_port, int) or not (30000 <= node_port <= 32767):\n                errors.append(\"node_port must be between 30000 and 32767\")\n\n        return errors\n\n    @staticmethod\n    def validate_agentcube_config(\n        workload_manager_url: Optional[str] = None,\n        router_url: Optional[str] = None,\n    ) -> List[str]:\n        \"\"\"验证 AgentCube 配置\n\n        Args:\n            workload_manager_url: 工作负载管理器 URL\n            router_url: 路由器 URL\n\n        Returns:\n            List[str]: 错误消息列表\n        \"\"\"\n        errors = []\n\n        workload_manager = workload_manager_url or os.getenv(\"WORKLOAD_MANAGER_URL\")\n        router = router_url or os.getenv(\"ROUTER_URL\")\n\n        if not workload_manager:\n            errors.append(\"workload_manager_url is required\")\n\n        if not router:\n            errors.append(\"router_url is required\")\n\n        return errors\n```\n\n#### 5.2 配置管理器\n\n```python\nfrom pathlib import Path\nfrom typing import Dict, Any, Optional\n\nclass ProviderConfigManager:\n    \"\"\"提供商配置管理器\"\"\"\n\n    DEFAULT_CONFIG_FILE = Path.home() / \".agentcube\" / \"providers.yaml\"\n\n    def __init__(self, config_file: Optional[Path] = None) -> None:\n        \"\"\"初始化配置管理器\n\n        Args:\n            config_file: 配置文件路径\n        \"\"\"\n        self.config_file = config_file or self.DEFAULT_CONFIG_FILE\n        self.configs: Dict[str, Any] = self._load_configs()\n\n    def _load_configs(self) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n        \"\"\"加载配置\"\"\"\n        if self.config_file.exists():\n            import yaml\n            with open(self.config_file, \"r\") as f:\n                return yaml.safe_load(f) or {}\n        return {}\n\n    def _save_configs(self) -> None:\n        \"\"\"保存配置\"\"\"\n        import yaml\n        self.config_file.parent.mkdir(parents=True, exist_ok=True)\n        with open(self.config_file, \"w\") as f:\n            yaml.dump(self.configs, f, default_flow_style=False, indent=2)\n\n    def get_config(\n        self,\n        provider_type: str,\n        key: Optional[str] = None,\n        default: Any = None,\n    ) -> Any:\n        \"\"\"获取配置\n\n        Args:\n            provider_type: 提供商类型\n            key: 配置键\n            default: 默认值\n\n        Returns:\n            Any: 配置值\n        \"\"\"\n        provider_config = self.configs.get(provider_type, {})\n\n        if key:\n            return provider_config.get(key, default)\n\n        return provider_config\n\n    def set_config(\n        self,\n        provider_type: str,\n        key: str,\n        value: Any,\n    ) -> None:\n        \"\"\"设置配置\n\n        Args:\n            provider_type: 提供商类型\n            key: 配置键\n            value: 配置值\n        \"\"\"\n        if provider_type not in self.configs:\n            self.configs[provider_type] = {}\n\n        self.configs[provider_type][key] = value\n        self._save_configs()\n\n    def get_provider_kwargs(\n        self,\n        provider_type: str,\n    ) -> Dict[str, Any]:\n        \"\"\"获取提供商初始化参数\n\n        Args:\n            provider_type: 提供商类型\n\n        Returns:\n            Dict[str, Any]: 参数字典\n        \"\"\"\n        provider_config = self.configs.get(provider_type, {})\n\n        kwargs = {}\n        if \"namespace\" in provider_config:\n            kwargs[\"namespace\"] = provider_config[\"namespace\"]\n        if \"kubeconfig\" in provider_config:\n            kwargs[\"kubeconfig\"] = provider_config[\"kubeconfig\"]\n        if \"timeout\" in provider_config:\n            kwargs[\"timeout\"] = provider_config[\"timeout\"]\n\n        return kwargs\n```\n\n### 6. 扩展性增强\n\n#### 6.1 插件系统\n\n```python\nclass ProviderPlugin(ABC):\n    \"\"\"提供商插件基类\"\"\"\n\n    @property\n    @abstractmethod\n    def name(self) -> str:\n        \"\"\"插件名称\"\"\"\n        pass\n\n    @property\n    @abstractmethod\n    def provider_type(self) -> str:\n        \"\"\"提供商类型\"\"\"\n        pass\n\n    @abstractmethod\n    def create_provider(\n        self,\n        **kwargs: Any,\n    ) -> BaseProvider:\n        \"\"\"创建提供商实例\n\n        Args:\n            **kwargs: 提供商初始化参数\n\n        Returns:\n            BaseProvider: 提供商实例\n        \"\"\"\n        pass\n\n    @abstractmethod\n    def validate_config(self, **kwargs: Any) -> List[str]:\n        \"\"\"验证配置\n\n        Args:\n            **kwargs: 配置参数\n\n        Returns:\n            List[str]: 错误消息列表\n        \"\"\"\n        pass\n\n\nclass ProviderPluginManager:\n    \"\"\"提供商插件管理器\"\"\"\n\n    def __init__(self) -> None:\n        self.plugins: Dict[str, ProviderPlugin] = {}\n\n    def register_plugin(self, plugin: ProviderPlugin) -> None:\n        \"\"\"注册插件\n\n        Args:\n            plugin: 插件实例\n        \"\"\"\n        self.plugins[plugin.name] = plugin\n\n        # 自动注册提供商\n        ProviderFactory.register(\n            plugin.provider_type,\n            plugin.create_provider.__class__,\n        )\n\n        logger.info(f\"Registered provider plugin: {plugin.name}\")\n\n    def unregister_plugin(self, plugin_name: str) -> None:\n        \"\"\"注销插件\n\n        Args:\n            plugin_name: 插件名称\n        \"\"\"\n        if plugin_name in self.plugins:\n            plugin = self.plugins[plugin_name]\n            ProviderFactory.unregister(plugin.provider_type)\n            del self.plugins[plugin_name]\n            logger.info(f\"Unregistered provider plugin: {plugin_name}\")\n\n    def get_plugin(self, plugin_name: str) -> Optional[ProviderPlugin]:\n        \"\"\"获取插件\n\n        Args:\n            plugin_name: 插件名称\n\n        Returns:\n            Optional[ProviderPlugin]: 插件实例\n        \"\"\"\n        return self.plugins.get(plugin_name)\n\n    def list_plugins(self) -> List[str]:\n        \"\"\"列出所有插件\n\n        Returns:\n            List[str]: 插件名称列表\n        \"\"\"\n        return list(self.plugins.keys())\n\n\n# 全局插件管理器实例\nplugin_manager = ProviderPluginManager()\n```\n\n## 实施计划\n\n### 阶段一：接口重构（1周）\n\n**目标**：统一提供商接口和返回值\n\n**任务**：\n1. 实现 `BaseProvider` 基类和相关数据类\n2. 重构 `KubernetesProvider` 实现新接口\n3. 重构 `AgentCubeProvider` 实现新接口\n4. 添加单元测试覆盖新接口\n\n**交付物**：\n- 统一的提供商接口代码\n- 重构后的两个提供商类\n- 单元测试覆盖率 > 80%\n\n### 阶段二：工厂和配置（1周）\n\n**目标**：实现提供商工厂和配置管理\n\n**任务**：\n1. 实现 `ProviderFactory` 工厂类\n2. 实现 `ConfigValidator` 验证器\n3. 实现 `ProviderConfigManager` 配置管理器\n4. 编写配置管理文档\n\n**交付物**：\n- 提供商工厂代码\n- 配置验证和管理代码\n- 配置管理文档\n\n### 阶段三：错误处理和重试（1周）\n\n**目标**：完善错误处理和重试机制\n\n**任务**：\n1. 实现自定义异常类\n2. 实现重试装饰器\n3. 更新提供商类使用新异常和重试\n4. 添加错误处理测试\n\n**交付物**：\n- 自定义异常类代码\n- 重试机制代码\n- 更新的提供商类\n- 错误处理测试\n\n### 阶段四：状态监控（1周）\n\n**目标**：实现状态监控和事件查询\n\n**任务**：\n1. 实现 `StatusMonitor` 监控器\n2. 实现 `EventMonitor` 事件监控器\n3. 添加日志查询功能\n4. 编写监控使用示例\n\n**交付物**：\n- 状态监控代码\n- 事件监控代码\n- 使用示例和文档\n\n### 阶段五：插件系统（1周）\n\n**目标**：实现插件系统支持扩展\n\n**任务**：\n1. 实现 `ProviderPlugin` 基类\n2. 实现 `ProviderPluginManager` 管理器\n3. 编写插件开发文档\n4. 实现示例插件\n\n**交付物**：\n- 插件系统代码\n- 示例插件\n- 插件开发文档\n\n### 阶段六：集成和测试（1周）\n\n**目标**：全面集成并进行测试\n\n**任务**：\n1. 更新 CLI 命令使用新接口\n2. 编写集成测试\n3. 进行端到端测试\n4. 性能测试和优化\n\n**交付物**：\n- 更新的 CLI 命令\n- 集成测试套件\n- 端到端测试报告\n- 性能测试报告\n\n### 阶段七：文档和发布（1周）\n\n**目标**：完善文档并准备发布\n\n**任务**：\n1. 更新 API 文档\n2. 编写用户指南\n3. 编写迁移指南\n4. 准备版本发布\n\n**交付物**：\n- 完整的 API 文档\n- 用户指南\n- 迁移指南\n- 版本发布说明\n\n## 影响分析\n\n### 向后兼容性\n\n**兼容性保证**：\n- 保留原有的 `deploy_agent` 和 `deploy_agent_runtime` 方法（作为废弃 API）\n- 保留原有的参数名称\n- 保留原有的返回值字段\n- 提供适配层兼容旧代码\n\n**迁移策略**：\n1. 标记旧方法为 `@deprecated`\n2. 提供迁移脚本转换旧代码\n3. 在文档中明确说明迁移步骤\n4. 保留旧 API 两个版本周期\n\n### 性能影响\n\n**预期影响**：\n- 接口重构：无明显性能影响\n- 重试机制：失败场景下增加延迟\n- 状态监控：定期轮询增加网络开销\n- 配置缓存：减少配置读取时间\n\n**优化措施**：\n- 使用连接池减少连接开销\n- 异步状态查询\n- 缓存配置和状态信息\n- 限制监控频率\n\n### 依赖变更\n\n**新增依赖**：\n- 无新增外部依赖（使用现有 Kubernetes 客户端）\n\n**版本要求**：\n- `kubernetes>=28.0.0`（保持不变）\n- `typer[all]>=0.9.0`（保持不变）\n- `pydantic>=2.0.0`（保持不变）\n\n## 风险评估\n\n### 高风险\n\n1. **接口变更兼容性**\n   - 风险：现有代码依赖旧接口\n   - 缓解：提供适配层，详细文档，保持旧 API 可用\n\n2. **状态监控性能**\n   - 风险：频繁轮询影响集群性能\n   - 缓解：限制轮询频率，支持事件驱动模式\n\n### 中风险\n\n1. **配置迁移**\n   - 风险：用户配置文件需要迁移\n   - 缓解：提供自动迁移工具，保留旧配置支持\n\n2. **插件生态**\n   - 风险：缺乏插件导致扩展能力未充分利用\n   - 缓解：提供核心插件集合和开发指南\n\n### 低风险\n\n1. **测试覆盖**\n   - 风险：新增功能测试覆盖不足\n   - 缓解：制定测试计划，使用 TDD 方法\n\n2. **文档完整性**\n   - 风险：文档更新滞后\n   - 缓解：文档与代码同步更新，自动化文档生成\n\n## 成功指标\n\n### 技术指标\n\n- 单元测试覆盖率 > 85%\n- 集成测试覆盖率 > 70%\n- 部署成功率 > 95%\n- 状态查询响应时间 < 1s\n- 重试成功率 > 80%\n\n### 质量指标\n\n- 代码审查通过率 100%\n- 静态分析无严重问题\n- 文档完整性 > 90%\n- API 一致性评分 > 9/10\n\n### 用户体验指标\n\n- 部署错误率降低 50%\n- 配置错误捕获率 > 90%\n- 用户满意度调查 > 8/10\n- 文档可读性评分 > 8/10\n\n## 备选方案\n\n### 方案 A：最小化改动\n\n**描述**：仅统一方法签名，保持其他实现不变\n\n**优点**：\n- 改动范围小\n- 风险低\n- 实施快速\n\n**缺点**：\n- 不解决错误处理问题\n- 状态监控仍然缺失\n- 扩展性未改善\n\n### 方案 B：完全重构\n\n**描述**：完全重写提供商系统，采用新架构\n\n**优点**：\n- 彻底解决现有问题\n- 更好的架构设计\n- 长期维护成本低\n\n**缺点**：\n- 实施周期长\n- 兼容性挑战大\n- 风险高\n\n### 推荐方案：渐进式增强\n\n采用本提案的方案，通过分阶段实施，在保证兼容性的同时逐步增强功能。\n\n## 结论\n\n本提案通过统一提供商接口、完善错误处理、增强状态监控、优化配置管理和扩展插件系统，显著改善了 K8s/AgentCube Provider 的架构。该方案在保持向后兼容性的同时，提供了更好的扩展性、可维护性和用户体验。\n\n建议按照实施计划分阶段推进，每个阶段都有明确的交付物和验证标准，确保项目质量和进度可控。","filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/cmd/cli/proposal.md"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.\n\nLSP errors detected in other files:\n<diagnostics file=\"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/cmd/cli/agentcube/services/k8s_provider.py\">\nERROR [46:32] \"CoreV1Api\" is not a known attribute of \"None\"\nERROR [47:32] \"AppsV1Api\" is not a known attribute of \"None\"\nERROR [56:23] \"ConfigException\" is not a known attribute of \"None\"\nERROR [53:24] \"load_kube_config\" is not a known attribute of \"None\"\nERROR [55:24] \"load_kube_config\" is not a known attribute of \"None\"\nERROR [59:27] \"ConfigException\" is not a known attribute of \"None\"\nERROR [58:24] \"load_incluster_config\" is not a known attribute of \"None\"\nERROR [70:18] Cannot access attribute \"status\" for class \"Exception\"\n  Attribute \"status\" is unknown\nERROR [71:36] \"V1Namespace\" is not a known attribute of \"None\"\nERROR [72:37] \"V1ObjectMeta\" is not a known attribute of \"None\"\nERROR [95:20] \"V1EnvVar\" is not a known attribute of \"None\"\nERROR [98:28] \"V1Container\" is not a known attribute of \"None\"\nERROR [101:27] \"V1ContainerPort\" is not a known attribute of \"N